  "body": "Reindexing all the transactions from the freezer takes a very long time. There's no need to hang the node in the mean time, we can do it in the background.\r\n\r\nOptionally, we should also have a flag that controls the timespan in which we're willing to index transactions (backfill or delete in the background). This has the potential of shaving off 1h worth of reindexing + 20GB worth of database size.",
